item.title: TryHackMe: Plotted-TMS
item.description: Here’s my write-up for Plotted-TMS, a CTF challenge created by sa.infinity8888. Write-up I deployed the box using TryHackMe’s interface and scanned the host using nmap: ┌──(kali㉿kali)-[~] └─$ nmap -sC -sV 10.10.167.242 Starting Nmap 7.92 ( https://nmap.org ) at 2022-03-06 08:24 EST Nmap scan report for 10.10.167.242 Host is up (0.088s latency). All 1000 scanned ports on 10.10.167.242 are in ignored states. Not shown: 1000 closed tcp ports (conn-refused) Service detection performed.
